{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7a6e8d008e","title":"宁波“万籁俱寂”需要打强心针","origin":"《批判文汇报的参考资料（二）上》（中华全国新闻工作者协会研究部、中国人民大学新闻系合编，解放军报社印）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1d2703983d","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"7a6e8d008e"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0dcfd4a5a8","name":"浙江"},{"id":"9e0c836ddc","name":"孙绍"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"107aa27c19","type":"title","text":"宁波“万籁俱寂”需要打强心针","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a6e8d008e"},{"id":"0c00804069","type":"authors","text":"浙江孙绍","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a6e8d008e"},{"id":"6ce260be8c","type":"appellation","text":"《文汇报》编辑同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a6e8d008e"},{"id":"bac664a480","type":"paragraph","text":"如果如您报所说：浙江省是“万籁俱寂”的话，那么宁波市就是“密云不雨”的了。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a6e8d008e"},{"id":"0d8edacaf0","type":"paragraph","text":"宁波不但未“放”未“鸣”，而且一些“代表”到杭州开了“省宣传工作会议”回来，还一声不响。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a6e8d008e"},{"id":"974c1f319f","type":"paragraph","text":"有些学校甚至还不准在时事学习时谈报纸上的“百家争鸣”问题，据说是恐怕要形成“混乱”。中共宁波市委迄今还无动静，这种情况和党中央的方针不符，事实上这样做也不能正确解决人民内部矛盾。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a6e8d008e"},{"id":"573de32488","type":"paragraph","text":"我建议领导上给我们宁波市来打一枚强心针。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a6e8d008e"}],"page":{"id":"72cced0d72","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7a6e8d008e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}